id: pmc-ztt5
title: "body-preview silently empty for real pm items: body not loaded (GH #27)"
description: "Items load via list-all --json / listAllFrontMatter which omit body. Fix: --include-body on CLI list-all; locateItem+readLocatedItem enrichment in extension when bodyPreview set. pm-cli PR #108 review."
type: Issue
status: closed
priority: 2
tags: []
created_at: "2026-06-05T09:41:08.752Z"
updated_at: "2026-06-05T10:35:20.855Z"
author: codex
resolution: "Fixed: CLI --include-body + extension locateItem/readLocatedItem (bounded concurrency)"
expected_result: "--body-preview renders real item body for pm items"
actual_result: "Both CLI and extension paths render real body, description fallback retained; verified"
comments[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-06-05T09:50:12.482Z",codex,"Fixed: CLI readPmItems adds --include-body to 'pm list-all --json' when bodyPreview>0 (verified --include-body populates body field in 2026.5.31+). Extension enrichItemBodies() re-reads bodies via public SDK locateItem+readLocatedItem (best-effort, per-item failure swallowed) when bodyPreview set. Unit test: fake pm bin returns body only with --include-body. Functionally verified both npx CLI and 'pm changelog generate --body-preview' render real body, fall back to description, no fork-bomb."
close_reason: Fixed in PR #30 (merged bf091b7)
